Household chemicals, oils and petroleum can be delivered to the Bellozanne waste oil reception. Contact us before you attempt to deliver any liquids to the waste oil reception.

- call 01534 445509
- email [dfi@gov.je](mailto:dfi@gov.je)

Household quantities of used cooking oil can be brought to the Household Recycling Centre, Gate 4, Bellozanne. Wait until the oil has cooled and poor it into an old container, take it to the Recycling Centre then decant it into the large white cooking oil recycling collector.

You can also leave unwanted household detergents and other cleaning chemicals at the Household Recycling Centre, Gate 4 Bellozanne. At the top of the slope, to the left.

